#lg B	cagbatuku


@(13-23=c2671.B.13) Snarling lion fiercely poised for the fight, …… snake spitting roaring at the enemy, great dragon …… holy incantations, whose knees never cease from running! Fearsome flood which no one can withstand, overflowing high water engulfing the banks!

$ (1 line unclear)
God, creative (?) personage who has no rival, foremost in heroism, who can rival you? @wDN{Numušda}, your face is that of a lion, and you have a muzzle like that of a fearsome @fsux{mušḫuš}.

