#lg C	jicgijal


@(25-32=c2671.C.25) Your arm is a battle net in (?) the land of those who do not practise agriculture; your claws are the claws of an eagle, grasping the wicked. No one dare oppose your authority. Your greatness and magnitude, surpassing all praise, and your utterances which cannot be dismissed

$ (1 line unclear)
My god, hand over to the king the disobedient lands! @wDN{Numušda}, hand over to prince @wRN{@wDN{Sîn}-iqīšam} the disobedient lands!

